Name: metadocuments
Version: 1.0.3
Summary: Library for defining structured documents (JSON, YAML) as classes. Created as a metaprogramming exercise
Home-page: https://gitlab.com/blissfulreboot/python/metadocuments
Author: Aki MÃ¤kinen
